title: C Tuckey
text:
C Tuckey ("" 1924 in <a href="Sydney">Sydney</a>, Australia) was a <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer in Australia's major competition, the <a href="New%20South%20Wales%20Rugby%20League">New South Wales Rugby League</a> (NSWRL).
Tuckey played for the <a href="Sydney%20Roosters">Eastern Suburbs</a> club in the year 1924.
